Move your headset more through the space while tracking the target. Use all directions - up and down, front to back, and side to side. This will help gather your surroundings better.
Move to an evenly lit space and try again. Avoid facing bright lights or direct sunlight.
Follow the target more closely throughout calibration. Remember to tilt your head from side to side, look left and right, and nod up and down. This will help Daydream gather your surroundings better.
